<footer class="gp-footer relative z-[2] pt-16 pb-10 md:pt-20 md:pb-10"
        style="background:var(--ink);color:var(--paper)">
  <div class="max-w-[1280px] mx-auto px-6 md:px-12">

    <!-- 3-column grid -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-[1.4fr_1fr_1fr] gap-8 md:gap-10">

      <!-- Brand -->
      <div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 font-[var(--display)] text-[22px] font-medium"
             style="color:var(--paper)">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 32 32" fill="none" class="w-7 h-7 shrink-0">
            <path d="M16 3 L16 29" stroke="#c5d99a" stroke-width="1.2"/>
            <path d="M16 9 Q9 12 7 19 M16 9 Q23 12 25 19 M16 16 Q11 19 9 25 M16 16 Q21 19 23 25"
                  stroke="#c5d99a" stroke-width="0.9" fill="none"/>
            <circle cx="16" cy="3" r="2" fill="#c5d99a"/>
            <circle cx="7"  cy="19" r="1.4" fill="#7a9a4a"/>
            <circle cx="25" cy="19" r="1.4" fill="#7a9a4a"/>
            <circle cx="9"  cy="25" r="1.2" fill="#7a9a4a"/>
            <circle cx="23" cy="25" r="1.2" fill="#7a9a4a"/>
          </svg>
          <span>Gopedia</span>
        </div>
        <p class="font-[var(--display)] italic leading-[1.4] mt-4 max-w-[360px]"
           style="font-size:22px;color:color-mix(in srgb,var(--paper) 85%,transparent)"
           data-ko-block>한 그루의 세계수 아래에서,<br/>모든 답은 어디서 왔는지를 안다.</p>
        <p class="font-[var(--display)] italic leading-[1.4] mt-4 max-w-[360px]"
           style="font-size:22px;color:color-mix(in srgb,var(--paper) 85%,transparent)"
           data-en-block>Beneath one World Tree,<br/>every answer knows where it grew.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Product links -->
      <div>
        <h5 class="font-[var(--sans)] text-[11px] tracking-[.25em] uppercase font-medium mb-4"
            style="color:color-mix(in srgb,var(--paper) 50%,transparent)" data-ko-block>제품</h5>
        <h5 class="font-[var(--sans)] text-[11px] tracking-[.25em] uppercase font-medium mb-4"
            style="color:color-mix(in srgb,var(--paper) 50%,transparent)" data-en-block>Product</h5>
        <ul class="list-none p-0 m-0 font-[var(--serif)] text-[15px] leading-[1.9]"
            style="color:color-mix(in srgb,var(--paper) 85%,transparent)">
          <li><a href="#values"    class="no-underline hover:opacity-70 transition-opacity"><span data-ko-block>철학</span><span data-en-block>Philosophy</span></a></li>
          <li><a href="#scenarios" class="no-underline hover:opacity-70 transition-opacity"><span data-ko-block>시나리오</span><span data-en-block>Scenarios</span></a></li>
          <li><a href="#quality"   class="no-underline hover:opacity-70 transition-opacity"><span data-ko-block>품질 지표</span><span data-en-block>Quality</span></a></li>
          <li><a href="#roadmap"   class="no-underline hover:opacity-70 transition-opacity"><span data-ko-block>로드맵</span><span data-en-block>Roadmap</span></a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Get started -->
      <div>
        <h5 class="font-[var(--sans)] text-[11px] tracking-[.25em] uppercase font-medium mb-4"
            style="color:color-mix(in srgb,var(--paper) 50%,transparent)" data-ko-block>시작하기</h5>
        <h5 class="font-[var(--sans)] text-[11px] tracking-[.25em] uppercase font-medium mb-4"
            style="color:color-mix(in srgb,var(--paper) 50%,transparent)" data-en-block>Get started</h5>
        <ul class="list-none p-0 m-0 font-[var(--serif)] text-[15px] leading-[1.9]"
            style="color:color-mix(in srgb,var(--paper) 85%,transparent)">
          <li><a href="https://toji.homes" class="no-underline hover:opacity-70 transition-opacity"><span data-ko-block>TOJI 홈</span><span data-en-block>TOJI Home</span></a></li>
          <li><a href="https://github.com/tojiuni/gopedia" class="no-underline hover:opacity-70 transition-opacity">GitHub</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Bottom bar -->
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-between items-start sm:items-center gap-2 mt-10 md:mt-14 pt-6 font-[var(--mono)] text-[11px] tracking-[.08em]"
         style="border-top:1px solid color-mix(in srgb,var(--paper) 12%,transparent);color:color-mix(in srgb,var(--paper) 50%,transparent)">
      <span>&copy; 2025 GOPEDIA</span>
      <span data-ko-block>세계수 아래 &mdash; 서울 &middot; 도쿄 &middot; 싱가포르</span>
      <span data-en-block>under the world tree &mdash; seoul &middot; tokyo &middot; singapore</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
